OL,3,CIsle of Man approves amendments to
OL,4,CAssisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man has voted to approve
OL,7,Famendments to the its Assisted Dying
OL,8,FBill - allowing it to be submitted
OL,9,Fonce more to become law.
OL,11,FThe bill was sent back to the Island
OL,12,Fby Westminster after the Ministry of
OL,13,FJustice (MoJ) said it was unable to
OL,14,Fgrant Royal Assent as it did not
OL,15,Fcomply with the European Convention on
OL,16,FHuman Rights.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
