CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781637075
OL,3,CIsle of Man approves amendments to
OL,4,CAssisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FIsland politicians have now voted on
OL,7,Famendments to the Bill which included
OL,8,Fchanges recommended by the MoJ,
OL,9,Fenhancing existing safeguards and
OL,10,Fensuring compliance with the European
OL,11,FCourt of Human Rights.
OL,13,FThe Manx government voted by a 3:1
OL,14,Fmajority for all amendments. In the
OL,15,FHouse of Keys, 16 members voted for,
OL,16,Fand six voted against and in the
OL,17,FLegislative Council five members voted
OL,18,Ffor, and one voted against.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
