OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781637075
OL,3,CIsle of Man approves amendments to
OL,4,CAssisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man was the first place in
OL,7,Fthe UK to legalise assisted dying in
OL,8,FMarch 2025 and has since been joined
OL,9,Fby Jersey in February 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
